Here, I've traced the values
of the first comparator bank.

12
00:00:38,520 --> 00:00:41,330
That should remind you of the difference
between a plus comparator and

13
00:00:41,330 --> 00:00:43,030
a minus comparator in
case you've forgotten.

14
00:00:44,160 --> 00:00:47,380
So insert your comparators
by typing pluses or

15
00:00:47,380 --> 00:00:50,470
minuses into appropriate
subsets of these empty boxes.
